qProperty.markdown:
**#[Self\-Service Customer Online Portal](3)**
In this scenario, imagine you are a customer of FinX and they offer an online portal where you can log in securely and access your account details including insights into how and why FinX is processing your personal data.  ^[
](inherit)^[FinX have leveraged the Qlik Associative engine to pull all your data from their multiple systems into one place allowing you to exercise your enhanced rights under the GDPR.](inherit)^[
·       Amend your personal data in case of any changes \(e.g. married name, change of  address\)
·       View and manage your marketing preferences
·       Exercise your right to be forgotten and close your account or request stop processing your data](inherit)^[· Download your personal data under the right of data portability 
 
Click the “Launch Self\-service Customer Online Portal” button below to see a concept of how this page might look after you have logged in.  For demonstration purposes, let's assume you have logged in as Yuki Whobrey.
](inherit)

qProperty.markdown:
**#[Customer Service Agent Portal](3)**
In this scenario FinX use a call center to manage their customer services. Imagine a scenario where you are the agent and have received a request from a customer wishing to exercising their rights under the GDPR.
 
Using Qlik's powerful search capabilities, the agent can search for and qualify the contacts details and Qlik’s Associative engine can pull all the relevant personal information into one place.  From here, the agent can use the information to kick off additional processes based on the request \(e.g. If there was a request for information, the screen could be templated with additional text explaining how and why they use personal data.  The agent could export this info as a PDF and send to an existing email or print and post processes\).  ^[
](inherit)^[They could also manage the customers marketing preferences, check accuracy of the data stored in relevant databases or audit additional processes to check if actions have been completed successfully.
 
Click the "Launch Customer Service Agent Portal" button below and search for “Whobrey, Yuki” or “Rim, Gladys” to see how a Qlik driven dashboard would be used by a call center agent.](inherit)
